{"tid":855139,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<首例>女網紅直播改編《義勇軍進行曲》違反國歌法即時被ban account","createTime":"2018-10-10T01:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T04:38:16.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d81601a0b96215afc4d0b6cfde248dc0dfb4fc68","tid":855139,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:01:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/3619274-134156333.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F3619274-134156333.html&d=pVqiA2KGJfIis%2Bm8MYXWdaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=c3e6b160\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/3619274-134156333.html</a><br />\n<br />\n內地網絡直播亂象不斷！有「虎牙抖音一姐」之稱的當紅女主播「Kelly莉哥」近日在直播期間，因為用古怪的方式唱《義勇軍進行曲》，被指違反《國歌法》，遭大量觀眾舉報，其直播間亦迅速被封。Kelly莉哥事後公開道歉，表示會暫停直播一段時間。<br />\n<br />\nKelly莉哥在內地直播界有極高人氣，曾在「抖音短視頻」上擁有4300萬多粉絲。她上月被「虎牙直播」用5000萬元人民幣（約5748萬港元）天價挖角，成為該平台的明星主播。惟她周日（7日）進行直播時，被指以充滿戲謔的姿勢，以及改編的曲調唱出《義勇軍進行曲》，還將短片放在個人專頁的頭版上，令她與虎牙成為眾矢之的。<br />\n<br />\n根據《國歌法》規定，奏唱《義勇軍進行曲》應當按照原本的歌詞和曲譜，不得以有損歌曲尊嚴的奏唱形式。在奏唱期間，在場人士應當肅穆，不可有不尊重的行為。"},{"pid":"6870663df050bb779831bdcd89c769c31d46ce86","tid":855139,"uid":55597,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/37a0c1af0cd95b5ca0df41271f859f95/tumblr_inline_ny5ykgMVBP1ta1qoy_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F37a0c1af0cd95b5ca0df41271f859f95%2Ftumblr_inline_ny5ykgMVBP1ta1qoy_1280.png&h=fe09d2e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4490950f7a12a97e251ce9095e990088193d2119","tid":855139,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"求 link"},{"pid":"c7f33a1af699cef1dbcf628ee0521ad66a306dd1","tid":855139,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6870663df050bb779831bdcd89c769c31d46ce86","tid":855139,"uid":55597,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T01:10:01.000Z","msg":